---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="About Us">
  <div class="bg-blue-200">
    <div class="py-30 flex flex-col justify-center px-5 text-center md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 m-auto">
      <p class="text-3xl font-semibold">Welcome! 📍</p>
      <div class="h-5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="text-lg">
        <p class="pb-5">I'm Jess, and like you I often find myself looking for an easy and effective way to find the best place to go grab a bite. So after realizing how tough that can be for cities that aren't as popular as some of the largest cities are, I decided to start this project to find places no matter where you are! Here's a list of the different types of food directories you can search for:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:px-15 lg:px-30">
            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <a href="https://wheresthepizza.com"><p class="text-xl font-semibold">🍕 Pizza</p></a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <a href="hhtps://wheresthechinesefood.com"><p class="text-xl font-semibold">🥡 Chinese</p></a>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>